<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_369_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>iebe</ex></expan> fraw als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Lorencʒen <expan>vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l4">etc / das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>Lorencʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l5">beſandt vnd <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ʒurede geſacʒt / der hat vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l6">wıe Jm vor etwıeuıl Jaren . etwıeuıl <expan>ſılb<ex>er</ex>s</expan> von eẅch bracht vnd be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l7">folhen wurd / eẅch ein gurtel ʒu <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> / dıe machet er daʒ <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l8">gürtel etwıeuıl mer ſılbers hett denn ir Jm ſchıket / Das teͣt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l9">er eẅch darnach oft ʒuwıſſen vnd hett <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> geſehen / daʒ Jr dıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l10">gürtel gelöſet vnd Jm ſein gelt geben hett / do des niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l11">geſcheͣhe vnd er ſeins gelts nıht <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> empern möcht / . do hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l12">er dıe gürteln von ſeinr notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan> / vnd ſey des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l13">ʒu ſcheden <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wan als er dıe gürteln nach <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l14">gemacht hett / do <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> ſıe niht yeds manns kawff daʒ er dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l15">an <expan>v<ex>er</ex>lıeſen</expan> müſt / wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> deẅht eẅch daʒ Jr <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l16">dem <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> ıcht <expan>ʒuſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett ſo <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l17"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt . <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l18"><expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l19">wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> ſo <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ıſt on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_line_1577280319342_3709">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_369_r1l22"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>E<ex>pi</ex>ph<ex>an</ex>ıa</expan> <expan>dom<ex>in</ex>j</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_369" id="183v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Barbara, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Görgen Schenken zu Geyrn
                                <expan>wirtin<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>iebe</ex></expan> fraw, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Lorenczen
                                <expan>Vett<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Lorencze<ex>n</ex></expan> für uns besandt und
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ernstl<ex>ich</ex></expan> zu rede gesaczt; der hat uns
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, wie im vor etwievil jaren
                        etwievil <expan>silb<ex>er</ex>s</expan> von ewch bracht und befolhen wurd,
                        ewch ein gurtel zu <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan>. Die machet er, daz
                                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> gürtel etwievil mer silbers hett,
                        denn ir im schiket, das teͣt er ewch darnach oft zu wissen und hett
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gesehen, daz ir die gürtel gelöset und
                        im sein gelt geben hett. Do des niht gescheͣhe und er seins gelts niht
                                <expan>leng<ex>er</ex></expan> empern möcht, do hab er die gürteln
                        von seinr notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>kawft</expan> und sey des zu scheden
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, wan als er die gürteln nach
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> gemacht hett, do
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> sie niht yeds manns kawff, daz er daran
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>liesen</expan> müst. Wie
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewht ewch, daz ir
                                <expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> zu dem
                            <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> icht <expan>zuspreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett,
                        so <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbotte<ex>n</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        slewnigs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> anheim ist, on
                            <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>e<ex>pi</ex>ph<ex>an</ex>ia</expan>
<expan>dom<ex>in</ex>i</expan>.</ab>
</div>
